translate portuguese jez13_dedcdede:

    # "Ivelisse is a little intimidating, but after a while, she smiles a lot and she seems pretty funny."
    "A Ivelisse é um pouco intimidante, mas passado algum tempo, sorri muito e parece bastante divertida."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:268
translate portuguese jez13_0ba3754f:

    # "And I can feel so much love between the three of them."
    "E consigo sentir tanto amor entre os três."

